{"tid":265506,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我成日見到IT 同CIVIL 有負面新聞, 但大電就冇乜負面新聞","createTime":"2017-05-31T16:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T17:09:17.000Z","uid":108039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15b7c0b088bf2cbb4709e533270fe22cb8207c54","tid":265506,"uid":108039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"我發覺成日都見到IT 同CIVIL 負面新聞, 但唔見大電有<br />\n不如一人一IT ,CIVIL ,EE 負面新聞張貼區 , 睇下邊個MAJOR 較多<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n30279civileecs1a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn30279civileecs1a9.jpg&h=b0e5a819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90423795b9a4a9b5217d7af8c03dff6f1bff4027","tid":265506,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我發覺成日都見到IT 同CIVIL 負面新聞, 但唔見大電有<br />\n不如一人一IT ,CIVIL ,EE 負面新聞張貼區 , 睇下邊個MAJOR 較多<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n30279civileecs1a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn30279civileecs1a9.jpg&h=b0e5a819&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣發表比較多D, 更易睇到個TREND"},{"pid":"03c90a6a9f2c0395294edfe55d71524a7bef79eb","tid":265506,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我發覺成日都見到IT 同CIVIL 負面新聞, 但唔見大電有<br />\n不如一人一IT ,CIVIL ,EE 負面新聞張貼區 , 睇下邊個MAJOR 較多<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n30279civileecs1a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn30279civileecs1a9.jpg&h=b0e5a819&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣發表比較多D, 更易睇到個TREND</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n【e-zone 專訊】2017 年過了不足半個月，全球科技公司傳出裁員消息，部分更已「落實」；即使是中國經濟因素、火紅的 VR（虛擬實境）技術也難擋經濟循環的巨輪。繼中興通訊（ZTE）本周初宣布裁員約 3,000 人後，儲存方案商 Seagate Technology（希捷科技）亦宣布將關閉中國蘇州工廠，並裁員 2,000 多人。<br />\n<br />\nSeagate 早在去年 7 月宣布全球重組計劃，縮減生產規模和改善營運效率，並打算在 2017 財年結束前裁走約 14% 員工、即 6,500 人；早在 2015 年 9 月，蘇州工廠已開始分批裁員，今次只是因應計劃提早把它關閉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/it-%E6%A5%AD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%8E%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B8%E5%85%8D/1222-17266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Farticle%2Fit-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25EF%25BC%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E5%2585%258D%2F1222-17266&d=%2BodAZQ8ljF%2BCdTIfQ6MkI6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=eeab55e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/it-%E6%A5%AD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%8E%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B8%E5%85%8D/1222-17266</a>"},{"pid":"0b85e1d2c6c60181da74340d5187d92861a7e23c","tid":265506,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"09ab595529f2237dd8692fab4ae8b8bc3ab3e9b1","tid":265506,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"個個it前輩都話生仔唔好比佢做it ，大家都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第時到我上位做族長，第一時間踢晒班it 狗出族譜。"},{"pid":"56530487692709fc90abbe9e82e5abac3943966d","tid":265506,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:25:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港大電王WKLee 唔敢入呢個POST</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f49a7d140f7d40e24c9b02ea14e2918238a66a","tid":265506,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201